															 Events Cable and Sound LLC (E.C.S.) is a full service, nation-wide audio and video company providing event multi-media solutions and media/press center services.  Our #1 job is media support. 
																	 
																	For over 15 years E.C.S. has provided media support and event services for some of golf's biggest events.   
																	 
																	Our clients include: 
																		The U.S.G.A. 
																		The PGA Tour, The Champions Tour 
																		The LPGA Tour, 
																		The World Golf Championships 
																		Numerous other events and made for TV Golf Specials 
																	 
																	We constantly strive to help make the media coverage of Professional Golf and other events the best it can be.   
																	 
																	Please see our  SERVICES?PAGE  to learn more about our products and services. 
																	 
														 
													 
												 
											 
										 
									 
									  
									   
								 
								 
									  
									 
										 
											  
										 
									 
								 
								 
									 
										 
											 
												 
													 
														 
															 
																 
																	 
																		 
																			 
																	 
																	 
																		 
																			 
																	 
																	 
																		 
